00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:14.799
This is my greenhouse.

00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:17.200
This

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:18.680
is a gardenia.

00:01:19.959 --> 00:01:22.400
Before it blooms in midsummer,
it needs plenty of water.

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:24.040
After it blooms,

00:01:24.439 --> 00:01:25.560
you should water it less.

00:01:30.959 --> 00:01:31.640
This flower

00:01:32.840 --> 00:01:33.959
is called a hydrangea.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.159
It loves shade and avoids sun.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.159
It likes moisture but not flooding.

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:40.959
It needs frequent watering,

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:44.079
but never too much at once.

00:01:47.959 --> 00:01:48.480
This flower

00:01:49.719 --> 00:01:51.159
is my favorite.

00:01:53.359 --> 00:01:54.560
It's called forget-me-not.

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:03.000
Because even in winter,

00:02:03.799 --> 00:02:04.879
it still blooms,

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:06.640
making it the most resilient flower.

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:11.080
Are you're telling me all this

00:02:13.599 --> 00:02:15.599
because you want me
to help you take care of them?

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:27.280
I just wanted to show you

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:29.039
my favorite flowers.

00:02:30.840 --> 00:02:32.080
Besides, with me around,

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:34.240
why would I need your help?

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.000
I'm more than willing

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:40.039
to be your gardener.

00:02:41.599 --> 00:02:42.800
Then let me test you.

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:44.879
The hydrangea I mentioned,

00:02:45.580 --> 00:02:46.400
how should you tend to it?

00:02:50.159 --> 00:02:52.360
I knew you didn't memorize it.

00:02:54.159 --> 00:02:55.599
When we get back tonight,

00:02:56.439 --> 00:02:57.599
I'll write down all the flowers

00:02:58.639 --> 00:02:59.840
in a notebook.

00:03:02.199 --> 00:03:03.639
You'd better memorize them.

00:03:05.439 --> 00:03:07.039
Looks like to win your heart,

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:08.319
I need to

00:03:08.639 --> 00:03:09.759
be dedicated.

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:14.240
You smooth talker.

00:03:22.199 --> 00:03:23.159
I recognize this flower.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.159
Magnolia.

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:29.759
The flower language of magnolia is

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:32.599
pure and sincere love.

00:03:34.960 --> 00:03:35.840
When the magnolia blooms,

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:38.400
you're the only one in my eyes.

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:02.680
So it's only a matter of time

00:04:04.639 --> 00:04:05.879
until the fall of Wujian.

00:04:07.879 --> 00:04:08.639
A century ago,

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:11.000
the First Master foresaw this disaster.

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:14.199
So he put the Chi and Mei pearls
into two humans.

00:04:14.599 --> 00:04:16.240
That way, you and Li Motong

00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:17.800
could draw strength from them.

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.200
And more importantly,

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.040
so that the two of you

00:04:22.839 --> 00:04:24.000
could unite to save the day.

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:26.040
So Li Motong and I

00:04:27.839 --> 00:04:30.040
were nothing but Father's pawns.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:32.759
Does he know?

00:04:39.439 --> 00:04:41.680
Now, for Miss Lu's sake,

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:43.160
Li Motong
is willing to give up his life,

00:04:43.160 --> 00:04:44.160
refusing to take the Mei pearl.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.839
All I can do is take a bet

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:48.759
on whether Lu Huayan
would sacrifice herself for Li Motong

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:50.040
and remove the Mei pearl.

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:51.759
So…

00:04:54.079 --> 00:04:56.000
who will truly save Wujian?

00:05:21.079 --> 00:05:21.879
Boss.

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:24.319
Have you found them?

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:26.120
I've searched everywhere,

00:05:26.199 --> 00:05:27.120
