00:05:29.800 --> 00:05:30.800
Work harder on the search.

00:05:31.079 --> 00:05:31.879
Search the whole city.

00:05:32.879 --> 00:05:33.720
Boss, where are you going?

00:05:49.319 --> 00:05:50.399
(If the Mei pearl stays within you,)

00:05:50.879 --> 00:05:52.279
(he can't return to Wujian.)

00:05:52.879 --> 00:05:54.120
(Not only will he die,)

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:56.120
(but the Wujian will perish as well.)

00:05:56.959 --> 00:05:59.879
(But I believe
you have the right to know)

00:06:00.480 --> 00:06:01.519
(and the right to choose.)

00:06:27.800 --> 00:06:28.560
Let go!

00:06:29.319 --> 00:06:29.879
Let go!

00:06:29.879 --> 00:06:30.600
I won't.

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:31.399
Let go!

00:06:31.399 --> 00:06:32.319
I said no!

00:06:39.560 --> 00:06:40.360
Lu Huayan.

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:41.879
Why would you

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:44.160
sacrifice your life for me?

00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:47.279
You've always been
the one protecting me.

00:06:48.360 --> 00:06:50.319
Let me protect you just this once.

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:52.720
Please, let me protect you for once!

00:06:53.560 --> 00:06:54.360
Lu Huayan.

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:57.759
I only wish for you to live well.

00:07:00.120 --> 00:07:01.319
But I can't

00:07:02.319 --> 00:07:03.680
