00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:08.279
If only one of us can live,

00:07:08.279 --> 00:07:09.959
I want it to be you.

00:07:09.959 --> 00:07:10.720
Lu Huayan!

00:07:12.279 --> 00:07:13.519
You once said

00:07:14.959 --> 00:07:16.680
