was destined to be a mistake.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:02.680
No.

00:08:04.959 --> 00:08:05.879
It wasn't a mistake.

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:09.600
Li Motong.

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:11.920
Just let me protect you this once.

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:15.519
I want you to live.

00:08:17.879 --> 00:08:18.879
